This is a call on President Muhammadu Buhari to save our souls in Oke Ogun area of Oyo State. Oke Ogun Area comprises of 10 local government areas; Iseyin, Kajola, Iwajowa, Atisbo, Saki West, Saki East, Oorelope, Itesiwaju, Olorunsogo and Irepo. These local governments are the most backward in Nigeria; we lack vital social amenities like federal institutions and even state. The only facilities provided by the Federal Government are the National Youth Service Corps Camp at Iseyin and Oke Ogun Polytechnic in Saki. Social amenities in Oyo state are concentrated in Ibadan, Ibarapa, Oyo and Ogbomoso; even the Okere Dam is now an abandoned project, if completed, it can provide jobs to scores of jobless youths and could provide power to South West states. Ibadan NSE inspects Moniya-Iseyin road project, charges… APC nominates Chukwuma to replace Moghalu as National… We discussed party cohesion, others at PDP governors meeting… Reconciliation: Makinde, Ibori, Olabode George, other PDP… The roads are so perilous, most especially the federal roads like Oyo to Iseyin and Saki. The oldest bridge in Nigeria is on this road, that is the Odo Ogun Bridge which was constructed in 1926 and it has claimed thousands of lives. We are making a passionate appeal to President Buhari and Governor Seyi Makinde to please provide social amenities  for us  to reduce migration of indigenes to urban cities. Doing these will increase the government’s internally generated revenue in all arms. Lasun Azeez, Iseyin. SHOCKING LIFE STORY!!! Abuja Man reveals (FREE) secret Fruits that Increased his Manh0d size and Lasting Power in just 7days… CLICK HERE TO GET IT!!! HERE IS HOW OVER 5000  NIGERIA MEN HAVE PERMANENTLY OVERCOME TERRIBLE BEDROOM PERFORMANCE DUE TO THIS RECENT DISCOVERY BY MEDICAL CONSULTANTS CLICK HERE NOW TO WORK FROM HOME ENTIRELY AT YOUR OWN CONVINIENCE AND GET PAID WEEKLY, DIRECTLY INTO YOUR SPECIFIED BANK ACCOUNT.REGISTRATION IS ABSOLUTELY FREE. LOOK!  YOU DONT NEED TO HAVE ANY EXPERIEN